headline: Examining the Changing Vistra Narrative After Earnings Growth and New Long-Term Power Deals
summary: The consensus analyst price target for Vistra has edged higher, rising from $228.26 to $230.71 per share. This change reflects a slight uptick in market expectations. This adjustment highlights renewed optimism about Vistra’s prospects amid notable shifts in the energy and utility landscape.
